contents: it is the purple that has a grey tint to it
it is not orange. it is also the lighter of the two browns
it is the deeper purple. not the one that is greyish
it is the bright pink. not the bright purple
it is green, not the ugly yellow green
it is neon pink. the brighter of the two pinks
it is the blue that is not purpleish
it is the more true blue. not the greyishone
it is grey. not the brown grey. not the green grey
